Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:04.78,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星たちの光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:12.46,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星たちの光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.79,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,一つ　二つ　鐘の音は響く心の中へと広く深く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.60,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,物語のような星の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.60,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,その中に细い线路を筑く 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:43.45,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,时间とともに时代は动く 流れる星は静かに动く 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:47.01,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,目を闭じて耳をすませば GOOD BYE 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:50.50,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,放て光負けずに しっかり今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.50,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,時を超え　誰かに届くまで 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:55.23,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,栄光の光はこの向こうにキミたちとつくっていくストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:00.73,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星達の光 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.95,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,古の思い願いが時代超えいろあせるコトなく届く 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:08.51,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,キラリ瞳に映る誰かの叫び 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.30,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,風に想いを　月に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.70,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,力ある限り生きてくんだ　今日も 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:16.21,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた夜空の星達の光 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.43,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,古の思い願いが時代超えいろあせるコトなく届く 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:24.50,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕らの想いもいつか誰かの胸に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:28.02,OP_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,光り続けよう　あの星のように 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:04.78,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:12.46,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.79,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一下 两下 钟声的余韵在心中回荡延展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.60,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,像故事般的星之滴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.60,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在其中构建出纤细的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:43.45,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,时代变迁 斗转星移  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:47.01,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,闭上双眼用心倾听 G O O D bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:50.50,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不输给光芒 坚决的穿越时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.50,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,传递到某人的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:55.23,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在荣耀之光的彼岸与你们一同创造故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:00.73,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.95,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的思念穿越时代传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:08.51,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,闪动的眼瞳中映现出谁的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.30,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,寄思念于风 诉心愿于明月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.70,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要拼尽全力的生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:16.21,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,举头仰望夜空繁星闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.43,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的思念穿越时代传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:24.50,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的思念总有一天会达到某人的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:28.02,OP_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,继续闪耀吧 就像那颗星星一样 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:39.19,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows who I really am
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:44.17,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I never felt this empty before
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:48.78,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I ever need someone to come along
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:53.74,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna comfort me, and keep me strong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:03.16,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,旅はまた続いてく  穏やかな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:13.45,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,月はまた新しい周期で 船を照らし出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:22.76,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,祈りをささげて  新しい日を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:32.25,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,鮮やかに  光る海  その果てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.44,ED_JP,,0000,0000,0000,,へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:39.19,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人知道我究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:44.17,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前从未感觉到如此虚无空荡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:48.78,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我需要有人来陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:53.74,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会安慰我并让我更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:03.16,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,旅程还在继续 安稳的日子也是一样 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:13.45,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,又一轮阴晴圆缺的月亮 映出了船的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:22.76,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈祷着 等候着新的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:32.25,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,直到那色泽鲜艳的光之海 得偿所愿为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.44,ED_CN,,0000,0000,0000,,へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们因无形而被畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因无形而被敬仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 的确感到强烈的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样挥下刀刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然冒出来把阿山踹倒 还要我们滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿年也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么蛮横暴力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们全部给我看好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题一:那个到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中间的那个臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是给之前死在这里的小鬼的贡品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿三
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么那个花瓶会被弄倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 我们玩滑板的时候弄倒的 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再犯同样的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也让你们被人用花供起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过这样威胁之后 我想他们应该不敢再靠近这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我再带新的花过来看你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我赶走他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来我就能过清静的日子了 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点投胎去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫黑崎一护 15岁 高中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里是开医院的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着有人被救活 有人却束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是否是因為这原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 自从我懂事以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见幽灵就像是理所当然一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不肖子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家不是规定每天晚餐时间是7点么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是对在外面拼命驱灵\N好不容易回家的儿子该有的对待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么理由\N破坏我们家团圆就只有遭到血的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那又怎样 你以為只有你能接触幽灵 跟他们说话而窃喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 我也不愿意生下来是这种体质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个别再吵啦 饭要冷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别理他们 游子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 夏梨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:05:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 让一个身心健全的高中男生\N每晚七点一定要回家本来就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护哥 又有一个新的人跟你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙什么时候跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么甩都还是会跟过来 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容易啊 一护哥的超高规格体质
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 有点羡慕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能感受到一点气息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不相信有幽灵存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？可是夏梨你不是能看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见的好像只有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他能不能看得到 只要不相信就等于是看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到空挡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 我睡觉去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 都怪老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥最近很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是最近看到的比之前更多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 那小子连这种事都跟你们说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不跟老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都年过40了 还用这么幼稚的方法进行沟通的老爸 谁会找你说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩儿他妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是思春期了吗 女儿对我好冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看先要把这张白痴一样的遗照给撕掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在所在的地点是空座町车站前一条马路的一角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据附近居民称
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午7点30分左右 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然轰隆一阵剧烈的地面晃动 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数栋大楼的墙面随之发生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤人数目前尚未统计出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 老爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要陪护病人 今天不回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 鉴定专家以及爆炸物专家已介入调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我什么都没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么很近 你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人问你话呢居然无视
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你看得见我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 刚才那一脚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你在说什麼我怎麼听不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是之前在路上碰到的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊 一般人应该是看不见我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过你在说什麼我听不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是【死神】
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 也就是说 你是死神 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大老远的从什么【尸魂界】\N跑来这裡驱散恶灵对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说刚才那个怪物就是恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是攻击那个小女孩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我先相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会相信啊 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明能看见幽灵 却不相信有死神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧 至今为止我还从未见过死神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是没有亲眼看到的东西 我是不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在不是看到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以相信你不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 少跟我玩死神的游戏 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吧 臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太没大没小了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缚道之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 你这是在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做【鬼道】
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是只有死神才会使用的高尚咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看我外表 我年纪起码比你大十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然叫我臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来早就该杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过规定指令之外的人是不可以杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该感谢我的 臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 昨天那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心 你要去的地方不是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尸魂界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟地狱不同 是个悠闲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送他去了尸魂界 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你们的话来说就是【成佛】
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死神的工作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让你这么轻率的小鬼也能明白 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做个简单的图解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 这世上有两种魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种叫做【整】 是普通好的灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你平时所看见的【幽灵】
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一种叫做【虚】
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不管活人 死者都会攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而吞噬他们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的【恶灵】
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止有什么疑问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 那我就先从你的画\N为什么会如此异常难看问起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就继续解释了 男爵阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们死神的工作有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是把【整】以刚才\N【魂葬】引导到尸魂界去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二种则是 把【虚】消灭 使其昇华
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个虚为什么会盯上那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能完全知晓它们的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻到了 特别好吃的灵魂的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟死神的味道混在一起 就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 第二只应该正在附近徘徊 没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快去驱散那第二只啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…从刚才开始 \N不知是什么原因 我完全感受不到它们的气息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感觉好像被某种强大的力量给阻断了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什麼啊 不是有狠大的声音么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个难道会错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是虚的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是游子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强的灵压
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然至今都没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏梨她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救 夏梨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏梨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鬼道困着居然还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事 退一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:15:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏梨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 那不是人类的力量能解开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是硬来 连你的灵魂都会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类可以自行解开鬼道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护哥 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏梨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏梨 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹们的灵魂还没有被他吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那傢伙在四处寻找灵的浓度高的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 白天那个虚的目标也不是那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才完全被你放出的魄动给抑制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我没有觉察到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没注意到虚盯上的其实是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是推测 只在你的体内流动的魄动 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你接触到的那个少女的灵魂为媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流到了外界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两隻虚从那个少女身上被你的灵魂所吸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切的目标都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退后 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我 那个孩子才被袭击是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我 夏梨跟游子都奄奄一息了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护哥 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你小子想要我的灵魂对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就跟我单挑决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的力量是比不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你以为把自己的灵魂给它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就万事大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去大家只能等着变成它的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救 你的家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成为死神
